name: Neon Origami
description:
Created by @fdoganis inspired by Neuromancer.

"And in the bloodlit dark behind his eyes, silver phosphenes boiling in from the edge of space, hypnoagogic images jerking past like film compiled from random frames. Symbols, figures, faces, a blurred, fragmented mandala of visual information.
[...]
Expanding—
And flowed, flowered for him, fluid neon origami trick"

William Gibson, Neuromancer (Sprawl, #1)
